@startuml
title UML State Chart Diagram

[*] --> Request

state Request
Request : entry / receive Video Suggestion Request
Request : do / identify User
Request : exit / identified

state RequestDecision <<choice>>
Request --> RequestDecision

state "Valid Request" as ValidRequest
ValidRequest : entry / gather Videos
ValidRequest : do / gather Videos from User Profile or Preferences
ValidRequest : do / gather Trending Videos from User's Area
ValidRequest : do / gather Videos with Similar Tags
ValidRequest : do / gather Videos from Similar Genres
ValidRequest : do / gather Promoted Videos
ValidRequest : exit / suggested Videos

state "Invalid Request" as InvalidRequest
InvalidRequest : entry / error Message
InvalidRequest : do / display Error Message
InvalidRequest : exit / return

RequestDecision --> ValidRequest
RequestDecision --> InvalidRequest

state Suggest
Suggest : entry / add Video Details
Suggest : do / add Thumbnails
Suggest : do / add View Counts
Suggest : exit / suggested Videos

ValidRequest --> Suggest

state Send
Send : entry / send Suggested Videos
Send : do / send Videos to User
Send : exit / completed

Suggest --> Send

state Complete
Complete : entry / completed
Complete : exit / end

Send --> Complete

@enduml
